org.sat4j.specs
Interface SearchListener

All Superinterfaces:
java.io.Serializable
All Known Implementing Classes:
ConflictLevelTracing, DecisionLevelTracing, DecisionTracing, DotSearchTracing, LearnedClauseSizeTracing, TextOutputTracing
public interface SearchListener
extends java.io.Serializable

Interface to the solver main steps. Useful for integrating search visualization or debugging. (that class moved from org.sat4j.minisat.core in earlier version of SAT4J).

Since:
2.1
Author:
daniel
